msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/tools_reference/settings_reference.rst:320
#: ../../../source/docs/tools_reference/settings_reference.rst:391
#: ../../../source/docs/tools_reference/settings_reference.rst:1165
#: ../../../source/docs/tools_reference/settings_reference.rst:1365
